// Kodex Dashboard
// Overview page showing Kodex health stats: total/verified topics, pending drafts, open flags,
// recent access history, and top missing topics.

FUNCTION StatCard(label, value, icon, color, link?)
  Render a metric card with label, numeric value, and icon.
  IF a link is provided, wrap the card in a router Link.

---

FUNCTION Dashboard()                                                    EXPORT
  CALLS: getDashboard (kodex-api)
  Read selectedProject from kodexStore.
  On mount (or project change): fetch dashboard stats via kodexApi.getDashboard.
  IF no project is selected, show a prompt to select one with a link back to Collab.
  WHILE loading: show a spinner.
  IF error: show the error message.
  ELSE render:
    - A 4-column stat grid with StatCard for Total Topics, Verified, Pending Drafts, and Open Flags.
    - A 2-column section with Recent Access (last 5 entries, linked to topic detail) and Missing Topics (top 5 with request counts).
